commit.message:
i386.c (bdesc_args): Use CODE_FOR_fix_truncv4dfv4si2, not CODE_FOR_fix_truncv4sfv4si2.

	* config/i386/i386.c (bdesc_args) [IX86_BUILTIN_CVTTPD2DQ256]: Use
	CODE_FOR_fix_truncv4dfv4si2, not CODE_FOR_fix_truncv4sfv4si2.

From-SVN: r180768
